These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, r&b
1. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of r&b is not to the right of the fan of r&b##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, superhero
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | rabbit | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | airplane | tram |

 #################################

 
